#

Gourmet Grilled Chicken Burger with Avocado Salsa and Spicy Lime Aioli

$15.99
750 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinDairy-Free

Tags:

GrilledBurgerHealthyComfort Food

Description

A succulent grilled chicken burger topped with fresh avocado salsa and a zesty lime aioli, served alongside crispy sweet potato fries.

Ingredients

  • Ground Chicken: 1 lb
  • Avocado: 2 ripe
  • Lime: 2
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Red Onion: 1/2, diced
  • Jalapeño: 1, minced
  • Mayonnaise: 1/2 cup
  • Sweet Potatoes: 2 large
  • Olive Oil: 3 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Paprika: 1 tsp
  • Cumin: 1 tsp
